EXTRACTED VALUE: This is a nice revision of last year's version. No, it is not an essential buy. If you have to be on the cutting edge, then you need to get this.
Although the game has minor flaws, it is largely an exciting racer that offers huge thrills and spills.
The gameplay is smooth as butter and the Skill Stick System is easily one of the best additions to sports games in recent years.
Despite the lack of online play and the humdrum combat system, LEGO Indiana Jones: The Original Adventures is a lot fun to play.
